<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.8.10">
<l>pōtamar celvak koḻuntu puṇartiru veḷḷaṟai yāṉai</l>
<l>mātarkku yarnta yacōtai makaṉtaṉṉaik kāppiṭṭa māṟṟam</l>
<l>vētap payaṉkoḷḷa valla viṭṭucit taṉcoṉṉa mālai</l>
<l>pātap payaṉkoḷḷa valla pattaruḷ ḷārviṉai pōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The karma of those who are devotees</l>
<l>who are able to reap the fruit</l>
<l>of the stanzas of [this] garland [of verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">spoken by Viṣṇucitta who was able to reap the fruit of the Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">with the words about fastening the Kāppu</l>
<l rend="indent">to the son of Yaśodā, superior among women,</l>
<l rend="indent">him of holy Veḷḷaṟai joined</l>
<l rend="indent">to the tender shoot of wealth [Śrī] resembling a lotus bud,</l>
<l>will depart.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
